{"id":312259206,"lang":"cpp","time":"2 years, 3 months","timestamp":1584166803,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"912 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/312259206/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Longest Substring Without Repeating Characters","memory":"265.6 MB","code":"class Solution {\npublic:\n    int lengthOfLongestSubstring(string s) {\n        int n = s.length();\n        s = \"#\" + s;\n        \n        int max_len = 0;\n        for (int i = 1; i <= n; i++) {\n            set <char> ss;\n            for (int j = i; j <= n; j++) {\n                ss.insert(s[j]);\n                if (ss.size() == j - i + 1) {\n                    max_len = max(max_len, j - i + 1);\n                }\n                else break;\n            }\n        }\n        return max_len;\n    }   \n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"longest-substring-without-repeating-characters"}
